page.title: 05CHRISTINA COLLINS
page.content: "On a school morning I get up at {6.45am.}I have a wash,get changed and then have my breakfast. I then have to help my mum with some work before I leave for the bus heading for school at{8.20am.}I arrive at school at{8.40am. I like school just a bit, but it is not my favourite thing during the day. I leave school to catch the bus at about{3.50pm. I arrive at home{4.10pm.}I help my mum do the washing up,drying up,clean the floor,polish,and then have to feed about 30 cats, because my mum owns a cattery.{I then have tea then do my {homework,}sometimes its easy but sometimes its hard.Then I watch{ {television.}Then I go to bed at{9.00pm On{Youth Club }nights I go to bed at {9.30pm,}I play snooker,table-tennis and we have{discos.}"
